    "en": {
      "name": "Vanquish Soul, Start!",
      "effect": "You can target 1 \"Vanquish Soul\" monster you control; add 1 \"Vanquish Soul\" monster with a different Attribute from your Deck to your hand. If a \"Vanquish Soul\" monster(s) you control would be destroyed by battle or card effect, you can reveal 1 \"Vanquish Soul\" monster in your hand instead. During your End Phase, if you control 2 or more \"Vanquish Soul\" monsters: You can Set 1 \"Vanquish Soul\" Trap from your Deck. You can only use each effect of \"Vanquish Soul, Start!\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
